Adventures is a roguelike action adventure role play game set in the dissonant state of Chechnya. The player must survive the harsh realities of a wartorn nation.


References for developers:

Python 3.4.1 docs:
https://docs.python.org/3.4/index.html#

MongoDB 2.6 docs:
http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/


Packages used include (http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/):
PyOpenGL
NumPy
PyQT4
